cite web|last=Contrada|first=Fred|title=Robert Downey Jr., Robert Duvall, Vincent D'Onofrio in Shelburne Falls as village is transformed into movie set for 'The Judge'|url=http://www.masslive.com/news/index.ssf/2013/06/shelburne_falls_is_transformed.html|website=Massive.com|accessdate=2013-06-14|date=2011-06-06|archive-date=2013-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130612033752/http://www.masslive.com/news/index.ssf/2013/06/shelburne_falls_is_transformed.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

