== 發行 ==

2014年9月4日，該片於[[2014年多伦多国际电影节|2014年多倫多國際電影節]]的開幕之夜上首次亮相<ref>{{cite news|last1=Pond|first1=Steve|title=Robert Downey Jr. Drama ‘The Judge’ to Open Toronto Film Festival|url=http://www.thewrap.com/robert-downey-jr-film-the-judge-to-open-toronto-film-festival/|accessdate=2014-07-28|publisher=thewrap.com|date=2014-07-25|archive-date=2014-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140729162827/http://www.thewrap.com/robert-downey-jr-film-the-judge-to-open-toronto-film-festival/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《大法官》於10月1日在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]舉行首映，地點位在[[比佛利山|比佛利山]]的[[美國電影藝術與科學學會|美國電影藝術與科學學會]]<ref>{{cite web|last=McNary|first=Dave|title=Robert Downey Jr., Robert Duvall Celebrate at 'The Judge' L.A. Premiere|url=http://variety.com/2014/scene/news/robert-downey-jr-robert-duvall-celebrate-at-the-judge-l-a-premiere-1201318342/|accessdate=2014-10-02|website=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2014-10-02|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006163421/http://variety.com/2014/scene/news/robert-downey-jr-robert-duvall-celebrate-at-the-judge-l-a-premiere-1201318342/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影於2014年10月10日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|last=McClintock|first=Pamela|title=Robert Downey Jr.'s 'The Judge' Gets a Fall 2014 Release|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/robert-downey-jrs-judge-hit-597220|work=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=2013-09-19|date=2013-07-31|archive-date=2018-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180128080204/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/robert-downey-jrs-judge-hit-597220|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 營銷 ===

2013年12月10日，[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]首度將電影劇照曝光於firstshowing.net上<ref>{{cite news|last1=Anderton|first1=Ethan|title=First Look: Robert Duvall Reprimands Robert Downey Jr in 'The Judge'|url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2013/first-look-robert-duvall-reprimands-robert-downey-jr-in-the-judge/|accessdate=2014-06-12|publisher=firstshowing.net|date=2013-12-10|archive-date=2014-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140613094659/http://www.firstshowing.net/2013/first-look-robert-duvall-reprimands-robert-downey-jr-in-the-judge/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年6月11日，電影的劇照於《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂週刊]]》發布<ref>{{cite news|last1=Breznican|first1=Anthony|title='The Judge': Robert Downey Jr. fights the law, and his father|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/06/11/the-judge-robert-downey-jr/|accessdate=2014-06-12|work=[[娛樂周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2014-06-11|archive-date=2014-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611234320/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/06/11/the-judge-robert-downey-jr/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨後，官方首支預告片於6月19日釋出<ref>{{cite news|last1=Atkinson|first1=Katie|title=In 'The Judge' trailer, Robert Downey Jr. proves you can go home again -- VIDEO|url=http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/06/19/the-judge-trailer-robert-downey-jr/|accessdate=2014-06-20|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2014-06-19|archive-date=2014-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140620162109/http://insidemovies.ew.com/2014/06/19/the-judge-trailer-robert-downey-jr/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。兩支國際預告片於9月11日推出<ref>{{cite news|last1=Anderton|first1=Ethan|title=Robert Downey Jr. Defends Your Honor in Two New 'The Judge' Trailers|url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2014/robert-downey-jr-defends-your-honor-in-two-new-the-judge-trailers/|accessdate=2014-09-11|publisher=firstshowing.net|date=2014-09-11|archive-date=2014-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911214904/http://www.firstshowing.net/2014/robert-downey-jr-defends-your-honor-in-two-new-the-judge-trailers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月17日時又釋出了另一支預告片<ref>{{cite news|last1=Anderton|first1=Ethan|title=One More Trailer for Robert Downey Jr.'s Family Drama 'The Judge'|url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2014/one-more-trailer-for-robert-downey-jr-s-family-drama-the-judge/|accessdate=2014-09-18|publisher=firstshowing.net|date=2014-09-17|archive-date=2014-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140921030035/http://www.firstshowing.net/2014/one-more-trailer-for-robert-downey-jr-s-family-drama-the-judge/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反響 ==

=== 評價 ===

影評界对电影的评价有好有差。[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的186篇專業影評文章中，88篇給予該片「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為47%，平均得分5.6分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_judge_2014/|title=The Judge (2014)|website=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2014-10-30|archive-date=2014-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027191451/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_judge_2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而基於另一影評匯總網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的39篇評論文章，其中12篇予以好評，6篇差評，21篇褒貶不一，平均分為48（滿分100），综合结果为「混合或中等評價」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-judge|title=The Judge Reviews|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2014-10-14|archive-date=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015232220/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-judge|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[影院評分|CinemaScore]]進行的調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「A-」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/10/gone-girl-dracula-judge-alexander-box-office-848782/|title=Monday Box Office: ‘Gone Girl’ Cements Week 2 Crown, Next Faces Pitt’s ‘Fury'|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|last=Bowles|first=Scott|date=2014-10-13|accessdate=2017-04-14|archive-date=2017-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170212071428/http://deadline.com/2014/10/gone-girl-dracula-judge-alexander-box-office-848782/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

影評人{{link-en|理察·羅珀|Richard Roeper}}给电影打分「C」，并评价道「我们观众居然根本不在乎电影里角色会怎么样」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/thejudge.aspx|title=The Judge (2014)|accessdate=2014-10-27|website=Richard Roeper & The Movies|last=Roeper|first=Richard|archive-date=2014-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027120101/http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/thejudge.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[衛報|衛報]]》的{{link-en|彼得·布萊德肖|Peter Bradshaw}}予以《大法官》中上的評價，寫道，「这部电影就像一个大杂烩，但却充满了如礼花般鸣放的丰富情感，看了之后十分愉悦。很显然，电影能够引来奥斯卡的评审」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/oct/16/the-judge-review-robert-downey-jr-duvall|title=The Judge review – part family drama, part courtroom gripper|website=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|last=Bradshaw|first=Peter|date=2014-10-16|accessdate=2017-04-15|archive-date=2017-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703184659/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/oct/16/the-judge-review-robert-downey-jr-duvall|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》的傑佛瑞·麥克納布寫道，「看看这复杂的剧情、若即若离的《[[金色池塘|金色池塘]]》式的感傷吧，如果杜瓦和道尼的演技能够再华丽一些的话，电影将会是乡村舞台上的一场盛大的狂欢」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/the-judge-film-review-hotshot-actors-duvall-and-downey-jr-make-a-compelling-case-9800115.html|title=The Judge, film review: Hot-shot actors Duvall and Downey Jr make a compelling case|website=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|last=Macnab|first=Geoffrey|date=2014-10-16|accessdate=2017-04-15|archive-date=2015-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150627023820/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/reviews/the-judge-film-review-hotshot-actors-duvall-and-downey-jr-make-a-compelling-case-9800115.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂週刊]]》的影評人克里斯·納什瓦提給出「B」的評價，並表示，「我不期望《大法官》開啟一個法庭驚悚片的新時代，但我樂見於小勞勃·道尼離開[[漫威電影宇宙|漫威宇宙]]和[[夏洛克·福爾摩斯|貝克街]]」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2014/10/16/judge|title=Movies – The Judge|website=[[娛樂周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|last=Nashawaty|first=Chris|date=2014-10-16|accessdate=2017-04-15|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314204515/http://www.ew.com/article/2014/10/16/judge|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===

《大法官》於北美的票房總額為4,710萬美元，其他地區3,730萬美元，全球共計8,440萬美元，而其製片預算為5,000萬美元<ref name="mojo" />。

在北美，電影於首映週末在3,003家劇院（每家劇院平均收入為4,368美元）中進帳1,310萬美元，位居該週票房第五<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekly&id=judge.htm|title=The Judge – Weekly|website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2014-10-13|archive-date=2014-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141019071443/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekly&id=judge.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他地區中，該片最成功的市場為俄羅斯、意大利和墨西哥，票房成績分別是440萬美元，299萬美元和208萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=judge.htm|title=The Judge – International Box Office|website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2015-01-13|archive-date=2014-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219191849/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=intl&id=judge.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

